title: Tucker Carlson praises Trump as 'most significant thing' to happen in US politics in 100 years
description: Tucker Carlson praised former President Donald Trump during his first interview since leaving Fox News earlier this year, claiming the former president "reoriented the Republican Party."

title: Dutch Prime Minister Mark Rutte resigns after almost more than a decade in office
description: The Dutch Prime Minister issued his resignation from office on Saturday, bringing an end to one of the country's longest-serving political leaders in decades.
